      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-6"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "七海八千代……和泉十七夜……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101600,
      "motion": 200,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-8",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-7"
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "你是，东边的魔法少女吧……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_030.exp.json",
      "id": 715104,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-9",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-8"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "十七夜……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 715104,
      "motion": 300,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-10",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-9"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "你明明应该最能理解@我们追求解放的理由……为什么……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_021.exp.json",
      "id": 100200,
      "motion": 200,
      "pos": 2,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-11",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-10"
     }
    ],
    "nameRight": "八千代",
    "textRight": "真是个愚蠢的问题。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 100200,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-12",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-11"
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "你们以为十七夜@会放任你们为所欲为吗？"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_020.exp.json",
      "id": 715104,
      "motion": 200,
      "mouthOpen": 0,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-13",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-12"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "西边的人@少用一副了不起的姿态说话！"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 715104,
      "mouthOpen": 0,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-14",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-13"
     }
    ],
    "textBg": "shout",
    "textLeft": "你们根本不知道@我们经受了怎样的痛苦！"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_030.exp.json",
      "id": 100200,
      "motion": 100,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-15",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-14"
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "痛苦？"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 715104,
      "motion": 0,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-16",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-15"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "一个是作为魔法少女@所背负的宿命，"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 715104,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-17",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-16"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "另一个则是@生为大东之人的宿命。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 715104,
      "motion": 300,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-18",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-17"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "你这种过得很滋润的西边的人@是绝对不可能会懂的。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_021.exp.json",
      "id": 100200,
      "lipSynch": 0,
      "motion": 0,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-19",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-18"
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "…………"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_030.exp.json",
      "id": 715104,
      "motion": 0,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-20",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-19"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "我们还有十七夜@生来就背负着人生的负债……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 715104,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-21",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-20"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "那是早在我们出生前@就不断累积的历史，"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 715104,
      "motion": 300,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-22",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-21"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "以及出生前就被定下的评价……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 100200,
      "motion": 201,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-23",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-22"
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "这跟你们把其它人牵扯进来@根本就没有关系吧。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 715104,
      "motion": 0,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-24",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-23"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "光凭你这句话@就足够让我发火了……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 715104,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-25",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-24"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "你和十七夜是老相识的话，@应该要知道才对……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 715104,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-26",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-25"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "大东的人们心灵饱受摧残，@很多人也自暴自弃。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 715104,
      "motion": 200,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-27",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-26"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "被当成了神滨的累赘，@还要被人随心所欲地利用！"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_000.exp.json",
      "id": 101600,
      "motion": 100,
      "pos": 2,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-28",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-27"
     }
    ],
    "nameRight": "十七夜",
    "textRight": "嗯，我理解你的心情。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 715104,
      "motion": 0
     },
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_030.exp.json",
      "id": 101600,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-29",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-28"
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "我们东边的人常常因为@他人的眼光而受伤……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101600,
      "motion": 300,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-30",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-29"
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "因莫须有的罪名受到西边居民顾忌，@他们的尖锐话语更如万箭穿心。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101600,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-31",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-30"
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "我们没有被当作独立的个体看待。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_020.exp.json",
      "id": 101600,
      "motion": 400,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-32",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-31"
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "那些大人物也是如此。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101600,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-33",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-32"
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "小时候被邀请去游乐园@也只是用来宣传的面子工程而已。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101600,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-34",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-33"
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "期待着能有新工作的人，@在这之后也都陷入了痛苦。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101600,
      "motion": 200,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-35",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-34"
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "东边的居民被人们的偏见伤害，@又因高层的野心被揭开伤疤。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_030.exp.json",
      "id": 100200,
      "motion": 0,
      "pos": 0,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-36",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-35"
     }
    ],
    "nameLeft": "八千代",
    "textLeft": "十七夜……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_020.exp.json",
      "id": 715104,
      "motion": 0,
      "pos": 0
     },
     {
      "id": 101600,
      "motion": 0,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-37",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-36"
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "但“想要救赎”@并不能当做为所欲为的理由。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101600,
      "motion": 100,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-38",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-37"
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "我们生来就蒙受着不公的待遇，@对我们来说，"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101600,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-39",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-38"
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "你的所作所为@可能会让我们背负的债越来越多。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_030.exp.json",
      "id": 715104,
      "motion": 300,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-40",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-39"
     },
     {
      "id": 101600,
      "motion": 0
     }
    ],
    "nameLeft": "白翼",
    "textLeft": "十七夜，@我果然还是理解不了你呀……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 715104,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-41",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-40"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "丘比出现时，@我曾认为那是我人生的转折点。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 715104,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-42",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-41"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "我以为人在蒙受苦难之后，@也会得到同样多的奇迹作为报偿。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_020.exp.json",
      "id": 715104,
      "motion": 0,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-43",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-42"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "可结果却是这样……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 715104,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-44",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-43"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "哪怕能从其中一种痛苦中@解脱出来也好……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 715104,
      "motion": 200,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-45",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-44"
     }
    ],
    "textBg": "shout",
    "textLeft": "我这么想也没问题吧！@这样的任性也是原谅的吧！"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_030.exp.json",
      "id": 715104,
      "motion": 300,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-46",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-45"
     },
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_030.exp.json",
      "id": 715003,
      "motion": 0,
      "pos": 1
     },
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_030.exp.json",
      "id": 715004,
      "motion": 0,
      "pos": 2
     }
    ],
    "nameCenter": "黑翼",
    "nameLeft": "白翼",
    "nameRight": "黑翼",
    "textLeft": "撤退吧……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 715004,
      "motion": 300,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-47",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-46"
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "是……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 715003,
      "motion": 300,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-48",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-47"
     }
    ],
    "textCenter": "我知道了……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_020.exp.json",
      "id": 715104,
      "motion": 0,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-49",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-48"
     },
     {
      "effect": "fadeout",
      "id": 715003
     },
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_030.exp.json",
      "id": 100200,
      "motion": 0,
      "pos": 2
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "请记住，"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 715104,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-50",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-49"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "你们会摧毁@所有人的希望。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 715104,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-51",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101935/vo_full_101935-1-50"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "失去了妹妹的人，@想保护好友的人，"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
